Class JungGui

java.lang.Object

                      synoptic.gui.JungGui
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.awt.print.Printable, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer
public class JungGui
extends javax.swing.JApplet
implements java.awt.print.Printable

Shows how to create a graph editor with JUNG. Mouse modes and actions are explained in the help text. The application version of GraphEditorDemo provides a File menu with an option to save the visible graph as a jpeg file.

Author:
Tom Nelson Edits to display our graphs.
